text: Dems are 54% of the total ballots cast in the #CArecall. They added +356k ballots vs GOP's 189k ballots on Friday & have an over 1M lead in cast ballots. Indie voters are about 2/3rds Dem leaning by voter history. If this keeps up, Newsom probably wins by double digits. https://t.co/Q8bYXkkdPg
